data.description:
Price Drop Alert!!
Classic home w/ lots of character sits high on corner lot in Murry Canyon. New electric furnace. Upstairs are 2 bedrooms, lg. office/den, spacious bathroom, living room w/ original wood floors & wood stove, upgraded kitchen, formal dining room, & mud room. Basement offers 1 more bedroom, full bath, kitchenette, lg. family room, & 1-car garage w/ outside entrance. Basement can be used as its own living space or combined for a 3 to 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home.
